      • filter

        public Collection<String> filter(int minAssays,
                        double minConf4,
                        double minConf9,
                        double minFunc)
        Filters the bioactivities in order to keep only those matching minimum requirements.
        Parameters:
        minAssays - minimum number of assays performed.
        minConf4 - minimum fraction of assays with confidence 4 or higher.
        minConf9 - minimum fraction of assays with confidence 9.
        minFunc - minimum fraction of functional assays.
        Returns:
        a collection of ChEMBL IDs which passed the filter.
